	   <tr><td colspan=2>There are 7 levels in the tower - per the designer of the tower, level 6 is split in two (6a and 6b with a mirror between NOT needing a key, but the theme is same, and there's a return mirror to 6a under ramp of 6b).&nbsp;&nbsp;Also, Tserrina's Key is a master to the LEFT mirror on level 1, takes you to a 6 mirror room on level 7 (Tserrina's level).  The door near the mirrors is locked, can be picked 201 skill OR use key from level 6 to 7 to open it and gain access to the spiral stairs near Tserrina.  The rightmost of the 6 mirrors is being kept "unworking" for now (try it, it responds slightly differently than the other mirrors) for future expansion in the game and storyline (again - per conversation with developer on Test server one day).<br><br>FYI, we've killed Tserrina 7 times now, 3 whips, 3 symbols, 1 staff, no robes (cry), but she dropped both her shortcut key, and the mage only handheld item every time.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
